    <section class="ABOUT">
        <div class="about-name">
          <div>
            <h2>About Our Gallery Name</h2>
            <p>
              <span
                >Eclipse Atrium symbolizes the transformative power of art. "Eclipse" represents the rare and extraordinary interplay of light and shadow, while "Atrium" evokes a welcoming space for connection and creativity. Together, they define a gallery where art transcends boundaries, inspiring awe and unity.</span
              >
            </p>
            <p>
              <br />Eclipse Atrium is a name that reflects the transformative and unifying power of art. The word "Eclipse" symbolizes rare, extraordinary moments where light and shadow merge, much like the way art reveals hidden beauty and challenges perceptions. It embodies mystery, wonder, and the potential for profound transformation.

                "Atrium" conveys the idea of an open, inviting space where people gather to share ideas, experiences, and creativity. It represents connection, growth, and a sense of community—qualities that lie at the heart of the gallery’s mission.

            Together, Eclipse Atrium captures the spirit of a space where boundaries dissolve, innovation thrives, and art serves as a bridge between worlds, inspiring awe and sparking meaningful dialogue.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
              <span
                >Eclipse Atrium’s mission is to celebrate bold creativity and transformative expression by providing a space where art transcends boundaries and inspires connection. We aim to empower artists, engage audiences, and foster a deeper appreciation for the limitless potential of artistic exploration.</span
              >
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
                At Eclipse Atrium, we believe in the power of art to transform perspectives, evoke emotions, and unite people across cultures and experiences. Our mission is to create a sanctuary where artists can push the boundaries of creativity, experimenting with new forms and ideas that challenge conventions.

                We are committed to curating diverse, thought-provoking exhibitions and events that celebrate both emerging and established voices. Through immersive experiences, workshops, and intimate conversations with artists, we aim to engage audiences on a personal level, inspiring curiosity and dialogue.
                
                Beyond showcasing art, Eclipse Atrium strives to be a hub for community and collaboration. We support creators in their journeys by providing resources, opportunities, and an inclusive platform where their visions can shine. Our ultimate goal is to enrich lives by fostering a deep, lasting connection with the transformative power of art.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
