        <div>
          <h2>Sponsors</h2>

          <div>
            <h3>Lumina Ventures</h3>
            <p>
                Illuminating Art, Innovating Tomorrow <br>
                Lumina Ventures is a forward-thinking investment company that specializes in supporting creative industries and technology-driven solutions. With a passion for art and innovation, Lumina Ventures believes in fostering collaborations that bridge art and tech to craft a brighter future. Their sponsorship helps Eclipse Atrium deliver cutting-edge exhibitions and workshops that merge traditional artistry with modern technology, making the gallery a beacon of creative evolution.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Aurora Artisan Collective
            </h3>
            <p>
                Empowering Artists, Enriching Communities
                Aurora Artisan Collective is a global network of craftsmen, designers, and creators dedicated to preserving and evolving traditional artistry. They work to provide platforms and resources for artisans from underrepresented backgrounds, ensuring their voices and visions reach wider audiences. Their partnership with Eclipse Atrium enables the gallery to showcase a diverse array of global talent and bring culturally rich narratives to the forefront.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3>Ethereal Edge Studio</h3>
            <p>
                Designing Worlds, Inspiring Visions
                Ethereal Edge Studio is a boutique design firm known for creating breathtaking environments and immersive experiences. With expertise in event design, lighting, and architectural installations, the studio brings unparalleled aesthetic finesse to every collaboration. As a sponsor, Ethereal Edge Studio contributes its expertise to Eclipse Atrium's exhibits, ensuring the space remains an ever-evolving, visually stunning realm for art enthusiasts and creators alike.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
